<DOCNO> LA100694-0028 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 085847 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 6, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
