Macaulay. Executive producers Ted Hope and James Schamus. Cinematographer Joe 
DeSalvo. Editor Richard Arrley. Music Ludovico Sorret. Set decorator Andra 
Kanegson. Running time: 1 hour, 41 minutes. 
