FEDERAL COURT IN O.C. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 While I recognize the need for a federal courthouse in Orange County, (General 
Services Administrator Roger) Johnson's, (Sen. Dianne) Feinstein's and (Sen. 
Dennis) DeConcini's actions should be recognized for what they represent -- the 
liberal's credo of pork over principle (especially within weeks of a 
congressional election)! 
</P>
