</P>
<P>
 Comedy writer John Mayer, on preview screenings of "Star Trek: Generations": 
"Audiences have been most impressed with the scene where retired Adm. James T. 
Kirk rewards Capt. Jean-Luc Picard by passing him the official Federation 
