 When reader Chuck Hull of Simi Valley was driving with his wife and 3-year-old 
son, Jesse, they changed from one freeway to another. The merging lane went 
around a tight curve and led them to a major traffic jam with all cars stopped. 
</P>
<P>
 Jesse piped up: "Who turned off the freeway?"  
