<BYLINE>
<P>
By HOLLY J. WAGNER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The city's Redevelopment Agency has unanimously approved a developer's plan to 
build 22 single-family homes on land at the southeast corner of Alta Vista 
Drive and Central Avenue, next to the Alta Vista Country Club. 
</P>
<P>
 Development Director Joyce Rosenthal said homes in the project, to be built by 
