 Five residents of a house in the 19300 block of Pitcairn Lane were robbed at 
gunpoint Wednesday by two men who had said they wanted to rent a room, police 
said. 
</P>
<P>
 None of the victims, who range in age from 20 to 33, were injured in the 
robbery, according to Lt. Luis Ochoa. 
