received a telephone call early Wednesday from someone asking to see it. About 
11 a.m., two men arrived, one of whom identified himself as having made the 
earlier call. 
</P>
<P>
 One of the men showed a chrome, semiautomatic handgun as the pair forced their 
way in, police said.MARK I. PINSKY 
