<HEADLINE>
<P>
OVATION AWARDS SCHEDULED AT ALEX THEATRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Ovation Awards -- the trophies from L.A.'s first peer-judged competitive 
theater competition -- will be presented at the Alex Theatre in Glendale on 
Nov. 14 at 7:30 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Nominations in 24 categories will be announced Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 The event is sponsored by Theatre LA. Tickets cost $15-$100 and may be 
purchased through Tele-Charge at (800) 447-7400. 
</P>
