<P>
Business; Part D; Page 5; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
90 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD WATCH: INTERNATIONAL BUSINESS 
